data.description: ***THIS PROPERTY MAY QUALIFY FOR $5000.00 TOWARDS WITH THE CHASE  HOMEBUYER GRANT. May  qualify for 100% financing**  Gorgeous well-built raised home with high ceilings, open floor plan, & lovely porch convenient to downtown New Orleans &  lakefront.  Nearby Hynes Elementary-UNO campuses, Audubon Elementary-Gentilly, Ben Franklin High, NORD Rec Center, Lakefront Arena, UNO & SUNO college campuses, restaurants, shopping & more!  Beautiful solid maple cabinets, granite countertops, hardwood stainless steel appliances, double closets in primary suite, plenty of storage in attic & under house, rear yard access, off-street parking for up to 3 vehicles, fully gated, spray foam insulation in attic, hurricane proof windows, monitored alarm system and security cameras.  Exterior security cameras monitored by private security company included in $200 parcel fee. Under termite contract and flood insurance is assumable.
